2074.subject: BIO
2074.descrlong: Required lab course for BIO 320. Covers general laboratory techniques and theory in microbiology including isolation and identification of bacterial species from nature, Koch's Postulates, transformation of Escherichia coli, Ames test, analysis of auxotrophic mutants.  Lab course fee may be charged.
